MIGRATION_RISKS.md:
  40  - Database user: `gladiators_user`
  41: - Password stored in `.env` (same pattern as API key)
  42  - Local-only access (no public exposure)

  45  **Potential Issues:**
  46: - Password exposed in logs (unlikely)
  47  - Connection pool exhaustion

  50  **Mitigations:**
  51: - ✅ Password in `.env` (already git-ignored, same as API key)
  52  - ✅ Local-only connections (firewall blocks external access)

  54  - ✅ Proper user permissions (GRANT statements in setup)
  55: - ✅ No password in code or logs
  56  

  59  - UFW firewall blocks port 5432 from public
  60: - Password complexity recommended (but not enforced)
  61  

