SECURITY.md:
  22  - **API key:** Clash Royale API key is read only from the environment (`CLASH_ROYALE_API_KEY`). It is never logged (except a masked preview in one startup message) and never sent to the client.
  23: - **Database:** Credentials come from environment variables (`DB_PASSWORD`, etc.). The app coerces the password to a string so the driver never receives a non-string value.
  24  - **`.env`:** Loaded only on the server; never served or exposed to the browser.

